RelatedSentence: On May 15 , 2014 Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Belarus to Argentina Mr.Victor Kozintsev met with First Deputy Minister of Foreign Affairs of Argentina Mr.Eduardo Antonio Zuain .
During the meeting the parties discussed current issues of Belarus - Argentina cooperation in different spheres .

The sides considered the organization of visits exchange at different levels , the development of the legal framework of bilateral relations , promotion of reciprocal travels of the citizens , strengthening contacts between the countries in the scientific , technological and other spheres .
